\s Iyo mifungo yomwoyo wangu.
\p
\v 12 Vanoshandura usiku ave masikati; Vanoti, "Chiedza chiri pedyo nerima."
\p
\v 13 Kana ndine tariro, Sheori ndiyo imba yangu;
\s Ndakawadza nhovo yangu murima;
\p
\v 14 Ndakati kuhwiro, "Ndiwe baba vangu;"
\s Nokuhonye, "Ndiwe mai vangu nehanzvadzi yangu;"
\p
\v 15 Zvino tariro yangu iripiko?
\s Kana iri tariro yangu, ndianiko angaiona?
\p
\v 16 Ichaburukira kumazariro eSheori,
\s Kana zororo yavapo paguruva.
